Having so many film-recorded movies under the DVD-R section is such a waste of time.  How many times have I downloaded a film thinking it was from an original DVD (comments here even say it came from a DVD) only to find out the camera is moving during filming, sound is crap and so is the video (high activity scenes get pixelized).  If you want DVD quality like I did, don't waste your time with this one.
